Centralized Mini Project Registration System
Instruction For Students
1. Students are requested to carefully fill all the details. 2. Before pressing the submit button please re-check all details and don't hesitate to press 'Verify Data' button as many times to make sure everything goes well. 3. Details once submitted can't be modified. 4. You are allowed to register only once. 5. Abuse of the system will result in ban from registering mini-project course. 6. If you have met your guide before and discussed about project, you may add remark. 7. Fake remarks will not be tolerated
